description:
Detroit Rappers Sada Baby and Skilla Baby join the ladies for Lip Service and things get WILD! Stephanie and Gigi team up against Sada and Skilla for a trivia based sex competition. Who do you think wins? The guys also discuss topics such as keeping their pants on during sex, what makes a coochie good/bad, Sada banging his friends mom, and much more. Make sure to go stream Sada Baby's latest album 'Bartier Bounty 3' and Skilla Baby's latest project 'Me vs Me.' Enjoy!
